0:
SELECT MAX("Percent (%) Eligible Free (K-12)") AS highest_eligible_free_rate
FROM frpm
WHERE "County Name" = 'Alameda'	----- bird -----	california_schools
1:
SELECT s.School, f."Percent (%) Eligible Free (Ages 5-17)" 
FROM frpm f
JOIN schools s ON f."CDSCode" = s."CDSCode"
WHERE s."SOCType" = 'Continuation'
ORDER BY f."Percent (%) Eligible Free (Ages 5-17)" ASC
LIMIT 3;	----- bird -----	california_schools
2:
SELECT s."Zip"
FROM schools s
WHERE s."County" = 'Fresno'
AND s."District" = 'Fresno County Office of Education'
AND s."Charter" = 1	----- bird -----	california_schools
3:
SELECT s."MailStreet"
FROM schools s
JOIN frpm f ON s."CDSCode" = f."CDSCode"
WHERE f."FRPM Count (K-12)" = (SELECT MAX("FRPM Count (K-12)") FROM frpm)
LIMIT 1;	----- bird -----	california_schools
4:
SELECT s."School", s."Phone", s."OpenDate"
FROM schools s
WHERE s."FundingType" = 'Directly funded'
AND s."Charter" = 1
AND s."OpenDate" > '2000-01-01'
ORDER BY s."OpenDate";	----- bird -----	california_schools
5:
SELECT COUNT(*) 
FROM satscores s
JOIN schools sc ON s.cds = sc."CDSCode"
WHERE s."AvgScrMath" > 400
AND sc."Virtual" = 'Y'
AND sc."Virtual" != 'P'	----- bird -----	california_schools
6:
SELECT s.School, s.District, s.County, sat.NumTstTakr, s.Magnet
FROM schools s
JOIN satscores sat ON s.CDSCode = sat.cds
WHERE sat.NumTstTakr > 500 AND s.Magnet = 1
ORDER BY sat.NumTstTakr DESC;	----- bird -----	california_schools
7:
SELECT s.Phone
FROM schools s
JOIN satscores sat ON s."CDSCode" = sat.cds
WHERE sat."NumGE1500" IS NOT NULL
ORDER BY sat."NumGE1500" DESC
LIMIT 1	----- bird -----	california_schools
8:
SELECT s."NumTstTakr"
FROM satscores s
JOIN frpm f ON s.cds = f."CDSCode"
WHERE f."FRPM Count (K-12)" = (SELECT MAX("FRPM Count (K-12)") FROM frpm)
LIMIT 1;	----- bird -----	california_schools
9:
SELECT COUNT(*) 
FROM satscores s
JOIN schools sc ON s.cds = sc."CDSCode"
WHERE s."AvgScrMath" > 560
AND sc."FundingType" = 'Directly funded'
AND sc."Charter" = 1	----- bird -----	california_schools
10:
SELECT f."FRPM Count (Ages 5-17)"
FROM satscores s
JOIN frpm f ON s.cds = f."CDSCode"
WHERE s.rtype = 'S'
ORDER BY s."AvgScrRead" DESC
LIMIT 1;	----- bird -----	california_schools
11:
SELECT "CDSCode" 
FROM frpm 
WHERE "Enrollment (K-12)" > 500;	----- bird -----	california_schools
12:
SELECT MAX(f."Percent (%) Eligible Free (Ages 5-17)") AS highest_eligible_free_rate
FROM satscores s
JOIN frpm f ON s.cds = f."CDSCode"
WHERE s."NumGE1500" / s."NumTstTakr" > 0.3	----- bird -----	california_schools
13:
SELECT s.Phone, sat.sname, sat."NumGE1500" * 100.0 / sat."NumTstTakr" AS excellence_rate
FROM satscores sat
JOIN schools s ON sat.cds = s."CDSCode"
WHERE sat."NumTstTakr" > 0
ORDER BY excellence_rate DESC
LIMIT 3;	----- bird -----	california_schools
14:
SELECT f."CDSCode", s."NCESSchool", f."School Name", f."Enrollment (Ages 5-17)"
FROM frpm f
JOIN schools s ON f."CDSCode" = s."CDSCode"
WHERE f."Enrollment (Ages 5-17)" IS NOT NULL
ORDER BY f."Enrollment (Ages 5-17)" DESC
LIMIT 5;	----- bird -----	california_schools
15:
SELECT s.dname, s."AvgScrRead"
FROM satscores s
JOIN schools sch ON s.cds = sch."CDSCode"
WHERE s.rtype = 'D' AND sch."StatusType" = 'Active'
ORDER BY s."AvgScrRead" DESC
LIMIT 1;	----- bird -----	california_schools
16:
SELECT COUNT(*) 
FROM satscores s
JOIN schools sc ON s.cds = sc."CDSCode"
WHERE sc."County" = 'Alameda' 
AND s."NumTstTakr" < 100	----- bird -----	california_schools
17:
SELECT s.sname, s."AvgScrWrite", sc."CharterNum"
FROM satscores s
JOIN schools sc ON s.cds = sc."CDSCode"
WHERE s."AvgScrWrite" > 499
ORDER BY s."AvgScrWrite" DESC;	----- bird -----	california_schools
18:
SELECT COUNT(*) 
FROM schools s
JOIN frpm f ON s."CDSCode" = f."CDSCode"
JOIN satscores sat ON s."CDSCode" = sat.cds
WHERE s.County = 'Fresno'
AND f."Charter Funding Type" = 'Directly funded'
AND sat."NumTstTakr" <= 250;	----- bird -----	california_schools
19:
SELECT s.Phone
FROM schools s
JOIN satscores sat ON s."CDSCode" = sat.cds
WHERE sat."AvgScrMath" = (SELECT MAX("AvgScrMath") FROM satscores)
LIMIT 1	----- bird -----	california_schools
